    "from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\n",
    "\n",
    "def split_dataframe(df, ratio=0.9):\n",
    "    data = df[df.columns[0]]\n",
    "    label = df[df.columns[1]]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    train_data, val_data, train_label, val_label = train_test_split(\n",
    "        data, label, test_size=1-ratio, random_state=42, shuffle=True\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return train_data.tolist(), train_label.tolist(), val_data.tolist(), val_label.tolist()\n",
    "\n",
    "df = pd.read_csv(\"./train.csv\")\n",
    "train_data_path, train_label_path, val_data_path, val_label_path = split_dataframe(df)\n",
    "\n",
    "test_df = pd.read_csv(\"./test.csv\")\n",
    "test_data_path = test_df[test_df.columns[0]].tolist()\n",
    "\n"
   ]

    "class dataset(Dataset):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, image_dir, label_dir, transform=None, label_transform=None, is_test=False):\n",
    "        self.transform = transform\n",
    "        self.label_transform = label_transform\n",
    "        self.image_dir = image_dir\n",
    "        self.label_dir = label_dir\n",
    "        self.is_test = is_test\n",
    "\n",
    "        if isinstance(self.image_dir, pd.DataFrame):\n",
    "            self.image_dir = self.image_dir.values.tolist()  # DataFrame -> List로 변환\n",
    "        if isinstance(self.label_dir, pd.DataFrame):\n",
    "            self.label_dir = self.label_dir.values.tolist() if self.label_dir is not None else None\n",
    "            \n",
    "    def __len__(self):\n",
    "        return len(self.image_dir)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    def __getitem__(self, idx):\n",
    "        data_path = self.image_dir[idx]\n",
    "        label_path = self.label_dir[idx] if self.label_dir else None\n",
    "        \n",
    "        image = PIL.Image.open(data_path).convert('RGB')\n",
    "        if label_path is None or not os.path.exists(label_path):\n",
    "            label = None\n",
    "        else:\n",
    "            label = PIL.Image.open(label_path).convert('RGB')\n",
    "\n",
    "        \n",
    "        if self.transform:\n",
    "            image = self.transform(image)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        if self.label_transform and label is not None:\n",
    "            label = self.label_transform(label)\n",
    "\n",
    "        # Test 데이터셋일 경우 레이블을 반환하지 않음\n",
    "        if self.is_test:\n",
    "            return image\n",
    "        else:\n",
    "            return image, label\n",
    "    \n",
    "data_transform = torchvision.transforms.Compose([torchvision.transforms.Resize((256, 256)),\n",
    "                                                 torchvision.transforms.ToTensor(),\n",
    "                                                 torchvision.transforms.Normalize([0.5], [0.5])])\n",
    "label_transform = torchvision.transforms.Compose([torchvision.transforms.Resize((256, 256)),\n",
    "                                                  torchvision.transforms.ToTensor(),\n",
    "                                                  torchvision.transforms.Normalize([0.5], [0.5])])"
   ]
  },

    "class FCN(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self):\n",
    "        super(FCN, self).__init__()\n",
    "        #x\n",
    "        self.conv1 = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=3, out_channels=64, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(64),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=64, out_channels=64, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(64),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2)\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        #x/2\n",
    "        self.conv2 = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=64, out_channels=128, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(128),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=128, out_channels=128, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(128),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2)\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        #x/4\n",
    "        self.conv3 = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=128, out_channels=256, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(256),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=256, out_channels=256, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(256),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2)\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        # Conv 블록 정의\n",
    "        self.pool3block = nn.Conv2d(in_channels=256, out_channels=3, kernel_size=1, stride=1, padding=0)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        self.conv4 = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=256, out_channels=512, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1), \n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(512),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=512, out_channels=512, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1), \n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(512),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2) \n",
    "        )\n",
    "        \n",
    "        self.pool4block = nn.Conv2d(in_channels=512, out_channels=3, kernel_size=1, stride=1, padding=0)\n",
    "\n",
    "        self.conv5 = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=512, out_channels=512, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(512), \n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=512, out_channels=512, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1), \n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(512),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2) \n",
    "        )\n",
    "\n",
    "        self.conv7block = nn.Conv2d(in_channels=512, out_channels=3, kernel_size=1, stride=1, padding=0)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # Upsampling layers\n",
    "        self.upscale_conv7 = nn.ConvTranspose2d(in_channels=3, out_channels=3, kernel_size=4, stride=2, padding=1, bias=False)  # 2x 업샘플\n",
    "        self.upscale_pool3 = nn.ConvTranspose2d(in_channels=3, out_channels=3, kernel_size=16, stride=8, padding=4, bias=False)  # 8x 업샘플\n",
    "        \n",
    "    def forward(self, x):\n",
    "        # VGG16의 conv1, conv2, conv3 사용\n",
    "        x = self.conv1(x)\n",
    "        x = self.conv2(x)\n",
    "        x = self.conv3(x)\n",
    "        pool3 = self.pool3block(x)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # VGG16의 conv4 사용\n",
    "        x = self.conv4(x)\n",
    "        pool4 = self.pool4block(x)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # VGG16의 conv5 사용\n",
    "        x = self.conv5(x)\n",
    "\n",
    "        x = self.conv7block(x)  # conv7 이후 num_classes 채널을 가져옵니다.\n",
    "        upscale_32 = self.upscale_conv7(x)\n",
    "        sum_32 = upscale_32 + pool4\n",
    "        \n",
    "        upscale_16 = self.upscale_conv7(sum_32)\n",
    "        sum_16 = upscale_16 + pool3\n",
    "        \n",
    "        upscale_8 = self.upscale_pool3(sum_16)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        return upscale_8\n",
    "\n",
    "model = FCN().to(device)"
   ]
  },
  {

    "class UNet(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, num_classes):\n",
    "        super(UNet, self).__init__()\n",
    "        self.num_classes = num_classes\n",
    "        #x\n",
    "        self.encode1 = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=3, out_channels=64, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(64),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=64, out_channels=64, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(64),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True)\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        \n",
    "        self.down1 = nn.MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2)\n",
    "        #x/2\n",
    "        self.encode2 = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=64, out_channels=128, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(128),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=128, out_channels=128, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(128),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True)\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        \n",
    "        self.down2 = nn.MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2)\n",
    "        #x/4\n",
    "        self.encode3 = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=128, out_channels=256, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(256),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=256, out_channels=256, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(256),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True)\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        \n",
    "        self.down3 = nn.MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2)\n",
    "        #x/8\n",
    "        self.encode4 = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=256, out_channels=512, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(512),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=512, out_channels=512, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(512),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True)\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        \n",
    "        self.down4 = nn.MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2)\n",
    "        #x/16\n",
    "        self.encode5 = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=512, out_channels=1024, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(1024),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=1024, out_channels=1024, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(1024),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True)\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # Decoder\n",
    "        self.up1 = nn.ConvTranspose2d(in_channels=1024, out_channels=512, kernel_size=4, stride=2, padding = 1, bias = False)\n",
    "        self.decode1 = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=1024, out_channels=512, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(512),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=512, out_channels=512, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(512),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True)\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        \n",
    "        self.up2 = nn.ConvTranspose2d(in_channels=512, out_channels=256, kernel_size=4, stride=2, padding = 1, bias = False)\n",
    "        self.decode2 = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=512, out_channels=256, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(256),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=256, out_channels=256, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(256),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True)\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        \n",
    "        self.up3 = nn.ConvTranspose2d(in_channels=256, out_channels=128, kernel_size=4, stride=2, padding = 1, bias = False)\n",
    "        self.decode3 = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=256, out_channels=128, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(128),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=128, out_channels=128, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(128),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True)\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        \n",
    "        self.up4 = nn.ConvTranspose2d(in_channels=128, out_channels=64, kernel_size=4, stride=2, padding = 1, bias = False)\n",
    "        self.decode4 = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=128, out_channels=64, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(64),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True),\n",
    "            nn.Conv2d(in_channels=64, out_channels=64, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),\n",
    "            nn.BatchNorm2d(64),\n",
    "            nn.ReLU(inplace=True)\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # Final output layer\n",
    "        self.final = nn.Conv2d(in_channels=64, out_channels=self.num_classes, kernel_size=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "    def forward(self, x):\n",
    "        # Encoder\n",
    "        enc1 = self.encode1(x)  # x\n",
    "        x = self.down1(enc1)    # x/2\n",
    "        \n",
    "        enc2 = self.encode2(x)  # x/2\n",
    "        x = self.down2(enc2)    # x/4\n",
    "        \n",
    "        enc3 = self.encode3(x)  # x/4\n",
    "        x = self.down3(enc3)    # x/8\n",
    "        \n",
    "        enc4 = self.encode4(x)  # x/8\n",
    "        x = self.down4(enc4)    # x/16\n",
    "        \n",
    "        x = self.encode5(x)     # x/16\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # Decoder\n",
    "        x = self.up1(x)         # x/8\n",
    "        x = torch.cat((enc4, x), dim=1)\n",
    "        x = self.decode1(x)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        x = self.up2(x)         # x/4\n",
    "        x = torch.cat((enc3, x), dim=1)\n",
    "        x = self.decode2(x)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        x = self.up3(x)         # x/2\n",
    "        x = torch.cat((enc2, x), dim=1)\n",
    "        x = self.decode3(x)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        x = self.up4(x)         # x\n",
    "        x = torch.cat((enc1, x), dim=1)\n",
    "        x = self.decode4(x)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # Final output\n",
    "        x = self.final(x)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        return x\n",
    "\n",
    "model = UNet(num_classes = 3).to(device)\n"
   ]
  },

   "source": [
    "from torch.cuda.amp import GradScaler, autocast\n",
    "\n",
    "scaler = GradScaler()\n",
    "def train(model, train_data):\n",
    "    model.train()\n",
    "    running_loss = 0.0\n",
    "    for images, labels in tqdm.tqdm(train_data, desc=\"Training\", unit=\"batch\"):\n",
    "        images = images.to(device)\n",
    "        labels = labels.to(device)\n",
    "        optimizer.zero_grad()\n",
    "\n",
    "        with autocast():  # 혼합 정밀도 사용\n",
    "            outputs = model(images)\n",
    "            loss = loss_ft(outputs, labels)\n",
    "\n",
    "        scaler.scale(loss).backward()\n",
    "        scaler.step(optimizer)\n",
    "        scaler.update()\n",
    "\n",
    "        running_loss += loss.item()\n",
    "    return running_loss / len(train_data)\n",
    "\n",
    "def validate(model, val_loader):\n",
    "    model.eval()\n",
    "    running_loss = 0.0\n",
    "    with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "        for images, labels in tqdm.tqdm(val_loader, desc=\"Validation\", unit=\"batch\"):\n",
    "            images, labels = images.to(device), labels.to(device)\n",
    "            outputs = model(images)\n",
    "            loss = loss_ft(outputs, labels)\n",
    "            running_loss += loss.item()\n",
    "    return running_loss / len(val_loader)"
   ]

    "# Visualization of predictions\n",
    "with torch.no_grad():\n",

    "        if cnt > 5:\n",

    "        pred_images = images.to(device)\n",
    "\n",

    "        outputs = outputs.cpu().squeeze(0)\n",
    "        outputs = outputs * 0.5 + 0.5\n",
    "        outputs = outputs.numpy().transpose(1,2,0)\n",
    "        output_resize = cv2.resize(outputs, dsize = (512,512), interpolation = cv2.INTER_LINEAR)\n",
    "        cnt+=1\n",
    "        fig, axs = plt.subplots(1, 3, figsize=(12,4))\n",
    "        axs[0].imshow(images[0].cpu().permute(1, 2, 0).clamp(0, 1))\n",
    "        axs[0].set_title(\"Image\")\n",
    "\n",
    "        axs[1].imshow(outputs)\n",
    "        axs[1].set_title(\"Pred_256\")\n",
    "\n",
    "        axs[2].imshow(output_resize)\n",
    "        axs[2].set_title('pred_512')\n",
    "        for ax in axs:\n",
    "            ax.axis(\"off\")\n",
    "        plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "        plt.show()\n"
